{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1773351967549,"sessionID":"ses_31c036c7affe6dPx3n8MQ9tKUs","part":{"id":"prt_ce4038747001cbRcxDDiuCrjkT","sessionID":"ses_31c036c7affe6dPx3n8MQ9tKUs","messageID":"msg_ce4037da00016dc8KiTnLez8n4","type":"tool","callID":"toolu_vrtx_01WaguNZrb83YbKs54GVZY82","tool":"bash","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"git add src/commands/launch.ts src/commands/resume.ts && git commit -m \"feat(dep-graph): integrate dependency-aware scheduling into launch and resume\n\n- Build dep graph and validate before launching (error on cycles/dangling deps)\n- Display schedule plan showing streams and merge gates\n- Populate agent depends_on/depended_on_by/stream_index from graph\n- launchNextQueued now uses readyToLaunchAgents (dep-aware)\n- Add launchAllReady to unblock multiple downstream agents at once\n- Cascade failures to downstream agents via cancelDownstream()\n- Both launch.ts and resume.ts use dependency-aware scheduling\n- Store SerializedSchedulePlan in WaveState for persistence\"","description":"Commit dep-aware launch/resume integration"},"output":"[feature/dependency-aware-sequencing 8e802d1] feat(dep-graph): integrate dependency-aware scheduling into launch and resume\n 2 files changed, 163 insertions(+), 15 deletions(-)\n","title":"Commit dep-aware launch/resume integration","metadata":{"output":"[feature/dependency-aware-sequencing 8e802d1] feat(dep-graph): integrate dependency-aware scheduling into launch and resume\n 2 files changed, 163 insertions(+), 15 deletions(-)\n","exit":0,"description":"Commit dep-aware launch/resume integration","truncated":false},"time":{"start":1773351967533,"end":1773351967548}}}}
